Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}SELF-STUDY{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You really want to help her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why not? Isn't it weird?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are they even treating her like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bullying often happens for petty reasons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bad attitude or a bad glare is all it takes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she looked to me...\Nshe must've been asking for help.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's just because we just happened to be there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm warning you, I won't be siding with you on this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll just shift their target from her to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.21,0:00:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then what's she supposed to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who knows.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe she gets over it,\Nor maybe she changes schools..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or maybe a teacher notices and intervenes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we let her be until then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:00:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You really are stubborn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:01:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, I'm starting to get\Nreally tired of your attitude, so-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm just as scared too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get you, Hina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, isn't it weird?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To label people as right or wrong? It's just weird...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't just stand by silently.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.79,0:01:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it today I had to go to the agency...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit... I overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}13: ROCK NEVER ENDS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't mince words.\NWe did not meet the expected results.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The video barely got any views,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,which means no subscribers either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How bad would you say it is, Miura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest issue of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you should be more\Nrecognizable than you've ever been.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All the search engine trends point to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that should be translating into views.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But we didn't get any views.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Which must be our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We failed to advertise you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,O-oh no, that's not what I meant-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In an era when anyone can do it on their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,agencies cannot afford to grow complacent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If an artist sees no value in an agency,\Nthey'll just leave it. Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,True enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give us a little more time.\NWe'll find a way to counter this loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've never seen her like that before...\N- Yeah, that caught me off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Momoka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sorry. Gotta dip", she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She went home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But we said we were gonna practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's fine, let's call it a day.\N- We probably should.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Momoka-san probably realized.\N- Of course she did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Of course you didn't realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Realize what?\N- Remember what she said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We are getting popular, but\Nour song isn't. Meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an issue with the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura-san must've realized that's\Nwhat Momoka-san was gonna say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so she spared her from saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To not hurt her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you've got it wrong! We'll turn it around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That song was amazing!\NEveryone praised it so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Miura-san or Nakata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If compliments were enough\Nto sell, life would be a lot easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They say Van Gogh couldn't sell\Nbut a painting in his lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, people get influenced by view counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll even watch hollow garbage\Nas long as others say it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No one wants to watch stuff\Nno one else cares about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"not true"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When looking up gameplay for a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,which video would you click on, the one\Nwith 5000 views, or the one with a million?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that. It's pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THE NEXT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"This band keeps picking fights they can't win."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Fucking showoffs, they piss me off."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Go kill yourself, loser."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs86}LEAVE ME ALONE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck off! I refuse to lose to assholes like you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,who are such insensitive deadbeats you didn't\Neven bother to show up to begin with!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathe... breathe... breathe... breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Our concert's coming up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And DD has already sold all of their tickets...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they have...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A follow request?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's verified...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Made you look, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay for you to go out like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not {\i1}that{\i0} famous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your taste hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. We used to eat these all the\Ntime when we came back from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, let me treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do you want?\N- Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thought we'd clear up any misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I didn't become DD's\Nvocalist to spite you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mentioned I went to several auditions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait nevermind, that was after you dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't have told you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So what, you came here to brag?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That I wouldn't be here had I listened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That things wouldn't have turned\Nthis way if only I'd listened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm lying. That's only half true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Have you sold any tickets?\N- Not your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I do think it {\i1}is{\i0} my problem though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing a concert together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,WE'RE NOT TOGETHER!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura-san from your agency came to visit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She was asking if we could play on both days,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so that they could sell enough tickets to make it a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At the rate you're going, you're\Nbarely selling like a third of the tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're available on that date, so in\Nthe end the choice comes down to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So I at least wanted to know what\Nyou and your bandmates thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,By "nothing" you mean "stay out of my way"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you mean it as a sign of thanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what it means to sell.\NIt's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Something to cherish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it up and admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"I was wrong. You were right, Hina."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"I wish I had listened to you."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Expose yourself and live"... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tell me you were wrong,\NI'll come to your rescue anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- HELLO?\N- Sorry to call you so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really, everyone else has already been informed but,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,DD offered to play on both days
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so we get to compete against the same audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura-san told you so, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- She did, but where did you hear that?\N- Doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What does everyone think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We were never gonna stand a chance with\Nhow it was originally laid out, so isn't this good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we do it this way, it won't be a competition anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,this is just going to be a DD concert in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be the same as admitting defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I get you Nina, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm against it! Completely against it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think it is\Nthat brought us this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact we weren't wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To prove that Momoka-san's songs are powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it this far because we believed in that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But reality won't be so easily forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, we haven't\Neven sold a third of the tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even worse than our indie debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to take responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you expect to pay for it otherwise?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Pay...?\N- And I'm not talking about just the venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the advertising, the merch...\Nnone of it comes for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to avoid any losses in any way we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm to blame here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to grovel like that to DD as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we're groveling to DD!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! They're just lending us a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think DD is giving us a hand for free?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura-san had to grovel and beg them for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She begged them to help us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know that we don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that if I recognized I was wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,she would help us out anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I refuse to accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't grovel your head down like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me for who I used to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Expenses... Responsibility... Popularity...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it already! I know!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so, so, so, so frustrating!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs86}LEAVE ME ALONEEEE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nina?\N- Nina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I so weak and spineless...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was them, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I told you, didn't I?\NThat I wouldn't side with you on this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you hate me that much for doing it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know... everytime we talk\NI always get this uncomfortable feeling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You brandish your sense of justice, but the thorns\Nof your insensitivity only end up hurting others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You keep making me feel like I'm the bad guy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- And so that's when you broke up contact with her?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the kinda flashback\NI expected out of Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happened to the girl that got bullied?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird as it may seem,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,after a short while, she joined\Neveryone else in bullying me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She then told me in secret\Nthat I should just apologize to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they'll surely forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wouldn't need to keep suffering like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But I could tell she was shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She was still afraid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But you saved her, right? You're her savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...And that's why you dropped out of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you weren't wrong... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were wrong! No matter\Nhow you look at it, you were wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, come on! Look at how it\Nended up. That Hina girl was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...That's what I love about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I love your singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Rupa, Momoka, and Subaru feel the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, sto-!\N- It's fine, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean I love you like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our answer, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Miura-san and everyone else worked hard for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you better take responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, who am I kidding, I knew it was\Ninevitable things would end up this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Always does with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's who Nina is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're rejecting the offer?\N- Yes. We apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But they said that they wanted\Nto have a proper duel against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But it makes it look as if they're trying to rescue us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, we have to account for the customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}LETTER OF RESIGNATION{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We all agreed together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, we understand this may be a selfish choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And that it may cause damages to the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us the damages this would cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot promise when, but I promise\Nwe'll pay it all back someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please raise your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you tell me your reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard everything
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina of DD contacted me and told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thankful for your help, Miura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You went this far to make sure our concert wouldn't fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And even now I realize how rude it is to reject this offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sorry. For being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I had imagined that\Nthis would go against your principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Miura-san...\N- I guess I'm a failure too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The money and contract is our responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I approached you to\Nbegin with is because of who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}LETTER OF RESIGNATION{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to assist you with this at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- You switching agencies?\N- No, we were thinking of going freelance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like working here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want to do this on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\fs46}Is he mad?\N{\fs46}- Should've chosen her words better.\N{\fs66}- That's quite the naive outlook...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact me again in a decade\Nif you're still kicking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work for you as a freebie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We will! Thank you so much, Nakata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Up for some good old gyudon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not fooling anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,\Nthis is where we first met you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Beni-Shoga, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to make an oath by eating some beni shoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,After all beni shoga holds a\Nlot of value to you as a name,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it'd be a nice way to make an oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of oath?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That we're gonna keep at it with\Nthe five of us, and no one's quitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nothing left but to eat, then.\N- I like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one drink, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this city!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a place where I've met friends\Nwho let me laugh and cry as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Kawasaki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're basically forfeiting, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Like those baseball teams that keep losing the Japan Series.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoping for a miracle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, as if. Life's not like a melodrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you like melodramas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A-all I watch is "Detective Grandma on the Case"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You trynna pick a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, we knew this was gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew reality would be harsh.\NThat this wouldn't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rich coming from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the last one who thought this was gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it means we get to\Nsay we weren't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, after DD's concert yesterday,\Nwe received a bunch of comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But you told me to not look at the comments!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Woah, I love this".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why's everyone hating so much on this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"All the haters should shut up.\NIt's not about the numbers."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Give them some time, need to see where they go."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it'd be better if they stayed silent,\Nit goes to show there's still folks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They can tell we're serious then, Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I didn't realize you had gotten\Nthat good at playing the guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To think you've made it this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay for me to play it though?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You spent so much time training by the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look up, Nina! - Hina{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look to your left - Hina{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My left?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,TOGENASHI TOGEARI
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\i1\fs100}Made you look, idiot <3{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- That little...\N- Seems like a fun person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Hina doesn't want to fully break ties with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She went so far to make you apologize,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,she must be teasing you at this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like her {\i1}final boss{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Demon King of\NAnnoying Self-Righteous Dummies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But beating you would mean clearing\Nthe game, and she doesn't want it to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that meant to make me happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say it, it means I wasn't wrong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone... it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ehm... As you might all already know,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:19:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're supposed to be facing\Noff against Diamond Dust, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The results are already obvi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, thank you for coming today!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth is, we've been pretty self-conscious about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About wanting to win against Diamond Dust.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About not wanting to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back during the festival,\Nwe were just as serious too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a bit sudden, but let me talk about myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that okay, Rupa-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I was in high school, I tried\Nto save a girl from getting bullied.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The moment I made\Nthat choice, I felt... happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt at peace... for once, I loved myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a result of it, I became\Nthe one getting bullied,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And in the end I had to drop out of school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But never once did I ever think...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I regretted doing that,\Nor that I should've avoided it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's when I realized...\NI have no regrets!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because Momoka-san's song\Nwas there, it gave me strength,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Hina knew that very well-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hina also loved DD. She loved their music.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn't just my song alone. It\Nreached and touched so many people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Allow me to thank you\Nonce again for coming here today!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You came here today because\Nyou're willing to go against the grain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But let me tell you... I love people like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I'm gonna scream out\Nthat we're not gonna lose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That we weren't wrong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Bear witness! This is where it all begins!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are all the same, trying our best to live our lives.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have no place to belong,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So we fly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our fates intertwined, reverberating, cutting off all paths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I dedicate the rest of my life to singing with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No light, no air, like an isolated prison.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pain, the suffering, and all the scars, I hated it all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if my wings were full of holes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I were in the depths of hell,\Nif I could I'd still sing with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I flew away, wanting to disappear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now I don't want to disappear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I picked the flower and kept it,\Nwaiting for it to one day bloom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The version of me who wanted to disappear is no more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I'm glad to be alive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I met you, it finally bloomed,\Nour flower of fate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}FLIP'EM OFF!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Three, two, one...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}THANK YOU!!{\i0}
